// Headless probe for the HDR calibration example. CI machines have no HDR
// display, so this exercises the documented downgrade path: the scRGB-linear
// request resolves back to plain SDR (warn + degrade) and the calibration
// patterns render clipped through the byte-identical SDR pipeline. Frame 200
// leaves headroom for surface (re)negotiation and the first pattern to settle.
(
    setup: (
        fixed_frame_time: Some(0.05),
    ),
    events: [
        (200, ScreenshotAndExit),
    ]
)
